========================================================================
WHAT THIS BRANCH DOES
========================================================================

Adds online horizontal remapping, vertical coarsening, derived field
computation, and vertical reduction to E3SM for FME (Full Model
Emulation) training data generation (ACE/Samudra).

Key source files:
  share/util/shr_horiz_remap_mod.F90    -- CRS SpMV remap + apply_masked
  share/util/shr_vcoarsen_mod.F90       -- vertical coarsening math
  share/util/shr_derived_mod.F90        -- expression parser (TOTAL_WATER)
  components/eam/src/control/           -- EAM wrappers
  components/mpas-ocean/src/            -- 3 analysis members + horiz_remap
  components/mpas-seaice/src/           -- 1 analysis member + horiz_remap
  cime_config/testmods_dirs/allactive/fme_output/  -- testmod + verify

